1. Zenodo>Profile>GitHub:
	Turn ON the switch for the repository

2. Github>Repository>Code>Releases:
	Tag Version v1.0
	Release Title
	Description
	Publish

3. Zenodo>Upload>The repository release:
	Edit:
		Check Everything
		Upload Type: Software
		License: MIT
		Grants: Remove Grants
		Save
		Publish

4. Take DOI and add to README file (as button)

# Auto DOI generation for each subsequent version
